headline.print_headline: Video of Turkish Fishermen Saving Migrant Baby From Sea
headline.main: Video of Turkish Fishermen Saving Migrant Baby From Sea

snippet: Dramatic video, posted online on Friday, showed a Turkish fishing boat saving a baby from drowning in the Aegean Sea this week.
